cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.MM

This paper deals with deep learning and classification tasks using multiple modalities, which are common topics in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), natural language processing (cs.CL), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and multimedia (cs.MM). Given the focus on deep learning and classification, cs.LG is the most likely sub-category. However, the use of multiple modalities and the application to natural language and multimedia data suggest that cs.CL, cs.CV, and cs.MM are also likely sub-categories. Finally, the use of semi-supervised learning techniques may also make cs.AI a relevant sub-category.
